This is the beginning of His earthly ministry,

00:27:18.579 --> 00:27:21.579
and we find that these servants are there,

00:27:21.579 --> 00:27:25.579
I don't know all of the details and all of the circumstances,

00:27:25.579 --> 00:27:27.579
but I find that in the text of Scripture

00:27:27.579 --> 00:27:29.579
that Mary says to these servants,

00:27:29.579 --> 00:27:35.579
Whatsoever He, Jesus, saith unto you, do it.

00:27:35.579 --> 00:27:38.579
And this evening, I would say that the counsel

00:27:38.579 --> 00:27:42.579
that Mary gives to the servants in John chapter number 2

00:27:42.579 --> 00:27:45.579
is good counsel for every one of us this evening.

00:27:45.579 --> 00:27:50.579
Whatsoever He saith unto you, do it.

00:27:50.579 --> 00:27:52.579
I'm sure that you're familiar, just as I am,

00:27:52.579 --> 00:27:57.579
with the little catchphrase of the athletic company Nike,

00:27:57.579 --> 00:27:59.579
just do it.

00:27:59.579 --> 00:28:04.579
And the reality is that we see how they've used that

00:28:04.579 --> 00:28:06.579
and so on and so forth, but I think about

00:28:06.579 --> 00:28:09.579
the truth of God's Word in this verse of Scripture

00:28:09.579 --> 00:28:12.579
where she says, do it.

00:28:12.579 --> 00:28:17.579
You know, the reality is that we don't need to pray about obeying.

00:28:17.579 --> 00:28:19.579
When God has given us a command in His Word,

00:28:19.579 --> 00:28:21.579
it's not something that we pray about,

00:28:21.579 --> 00:28:23.579
it's something that we do.

00:28:23.579 --> 00:28:25.579
We simply obey Him.

00:28:25.579 --> 00:28:27.579
There are certainly things that we must pray about

00:28:27.579 --> 00:28:29.579
and we understand what those are,

00:28:29.579 --> 00:28:31.579
but when it comes to the commands,

00:28:31.579 --> 00:28:34.579
the obvious commands that God has given to us in His Word,

00:28:34.579 --> 00:28:37.579
there's no need for us to pray about those things,

00:28:37.579 --> 00:28:39.579
we simply do them.

00:28:39.579 --> 00:28:41.579
There's no need for delayed obedience

00:28:41.579 --> 00:28:43.579
in the life of a believer.

00:28:43.579 --> 00:28:46.579
We must obey immediately, right away,

00:28:47.579 --> 00:28:50.579
seizing the opportunity, not missing the opportunity,

00:28:50.579 --> 00:28:52.579
but obeying the Lord.

00:28:52.579 --> 00:28:54.579
This evening as we wrap up this mini-series

00:28:54.579 --> 00:28:58.579
within this greater series of doing what we ought to do,

00:28:58.579 --> 00:29:01.579
we find here this evening that Jesus,

00:29:01.579 --> 00:29:03.579
He walked and left us an example

00:29:03.579 --> 00:29:05.579
and I hope tonight that you could add,

00:29:05.579 --> 00:29:07.579
and I mentioned this earlier on,

00:29:07.579 --> 00:29:09.579
it's not an exhaustive list.

00:29:09.579 --> 00:29:11.579
There's so many other ways as we study through the Gospels

00:29:11.579 --> 00:29:13.579
that we see how Christ walked

00:29:13.579 --> 00:29:15.579
and I'm thankful that He walked with courage

00:29:15.579 --> 00:29:19.579
and with compassion and with honesty and with humility

00:29:19.579 --> 00:29:22.579
and I'm thankful that He walked there with wisdom

00:29:22.579 --> 00:29:25.579
and I'm thankful tonight for the example

00:29:25.579 --> 00:29:28.579
that He gave us of walking in obedience.

00:29:28.579 --> 00:29:32.579
And tonight I simply want to say this,

00:29:32.579 --> 00:29:34.579
if we examine our lives,

00:29:34.579 --> 00:29:38.579
we know what obedience looks like.

00:29:38.579 --> 00:29:44.579
We know what it is when someone disobeys what we've said.

00:29:44.579 --> 00:29:47.579
If you have children, no doubt there's been some time

00:29:47.579 --> 00:29:50.579
in your life of rearing children

00:29:50.579 --> 00:29:52.579
that you've given them some instruction

00:29:52.579 --> 00:29:56.579
and they just failed to obey the instruction.

00:29:56.579 --> 00:29:58.579
And sometimes you look at the children,

00:29:58.579 --> 00:30:00.579
as I did many times,

00:30:00.579 --> 00:30:02.779
over the years, and I would say,

00:30:02.779 --> 00:30:05.879
there's now a consequence for the disobedience.

00:30:07.179 --> 00:30:08.579
And you kind of look at it and say,

00:30:08.579 --> 00:30:10.819
you know, it's really just so simple.

00:30:11.719 --> 00:30:16.699
If you just obey, then you don't have to deal with this.

00:30:16.699 --> 00:30:20.499
And every time over the years of rearing children

00:30:20.499 --> 00:30:24.539
and dealing with that, every time I'd say those words,

00:30:24.539 --> 00:30:27.419
it was like the Holy Spirit of God would say to me,

00:30:27.419 --> 00:30:30.139
it's so easy, just obey.

00:30:31.499 --> 00:30:33.699
God's made it plain.

00:30:33.699 --> 00:30:35.739
He's given to us his word.

00:30:35.739 --> 00:30:37.019
It's not a problem with hearing.

00:30:37.019 --> 00:30:40.139
It's not a problem with having the word.

00:30:40.139 --> 00:30:43.779
It's a problem in our own lives of doing it, of obeying.

00:30:43.779 --> 00:30:45.879
And this evening, I hope that we could just make

00:30:45.879 --> 00:30:48.579
a commitment before the Lord that, you know,

00:30:48.579 --> 00:30:52.659
I'm gonna strive to live a life of obedience.

00:30:52.659 --> 00:30:54.699
I'm just gonna obey God.

00:30:54.699 --> 00:30:58.339
No questions asked, no, I'm not gonna take a poll

00:30:58.339 --> 00:31:02.379
of what the world's doing and what's commonly accepted

00:31:02.379 --> 00:31:04.619
and comparing myself amongst ourselves.

00:31:04.619 --> 00:31:07.059
No, I'm just gonna make a determination

00:31:07.059 --> 00:31:09.819
that whatsoever he saith, I'm just gonna do.

00:31:09.819 --> 00:31:13.499
I'm just gonna obey God because to obey is better.

00:31:13.499 --> 00:31:15.779
There's so many other verses that we could look at tonight

00:31:15.779 --> 00:31:18.339
with regard to the subject of obedience.

00:31:18.339 --> 00:31:23.339
It's an oft-discussed subject from this pulpit

00:31:23.419 --> 00:31:27.139
from various passages throughout God's word.

00:31:27.139 --> 00:31:30.159
Obedience, obedience, obedience.

00:31:31.139 --> 00:31:33.599
And let these words ring in your heart.

00:31:33.599 --> 00:31:37.179
Why calleth ye me, Lord, Lord,

00:31:37.179 --> 00:31:40.379
and do not the things that I say?

00:31:40.379 --> 00:31:41.219
Let's pray together.

00:31:41.219 --> 00:31:42.039
Father, we love you.

00:31:42.039 --> 00:31:43.099
We thank you for loving us.

00:31:43.099 --> 00:31:46.019
We thank you for the opportunity that we have

00:31:46.019 --> 00:31:49.859
to have your word and to know what you expect of us,

00:31:49.859 --> 00:31:51.039
what you've commanded us.

00:31:51.039 --> 00:31:53.539
I pray that you'd help us to be obedient, Lord.

00:31:54.539 --> 00:31:57.699
Help us not to excuse disobedience in our lives.

00:31:57.699 --> 00:32:01.059
Help us, Lord, to just make that commitment

00:32:01.059 --> 00:32:04.579
that we're going to live a life of obedience.

00:32:04.579 --> 00:32:08.099
I pray that, Lord, if you've put your finger

00:32:08.099 --> 00:32:10.659
on some specific area in our lives tonight,

00:32:10.659 --> 00:32:13.579
Lord, I pray that you'd help us to deal with that.

00:32:13.579 --> 00:32:17.459
I pray that you would help us to seek you,

00:32:17.459 --> 00:32:19.099
to seek to please you, Lord,

00:32:19.099 --> 00:32:21.459
through all that we say and all that we do.

00:32:21.459 --> 00:32:23.099
I pray that you'd bless our time of prayer.

00:32:23.659 --> 00:32:24.499
We thank you for the privilege

00:32:24.499 --> 00:32:26.099
that we have each Wednesday evening

00:32:26.099 --> 00:32:29.259
to review updates from our missionaries

00:32:29.259 --> 00:32:32.979
and to share requests of prayer

00:32:32.979 --> 00:32:36.979
and to rejoice one with another of answered prayer.

00:32:36.979 --> 00:32:39.339
And God, I pray that you'd bless our time of prayer tonight.

00:32:39.339 --> 00:32:41.059
We pray that you'd be honored and glorified

00:32:41.059 --> 00:32:42.139
through all that's said and done.

00:32:42.139 --> 00:32:45.219
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

00:32:45.219 --> 00:32:46.619
All right, anyone need a prayer?

